{"tid":386064,"cid":34,"subCid":0,"title":"【Orage台】最後的主線之龍就是自身化為主線之龍 Day106 3/9 【人中之龍6】","createTime":"2017-09-03T15:15:21.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-03T18:06:20.000Z","uid":122942,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"7e4b73780180e91aac87a9ea3bd6801ba9050d53","tid":386064,"uid":122942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T15:15:21.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://upload.cc/i2/5ADqP2.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi2%2F5ADqP2.gif&h=8c5a58f0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n大家好，我係Orage。 我會於每晚11點至2點開台玩遊戲同與觀眾聊天。<br />\n因為我極度3分鐘熱度，所以好少會一直玩同一隻Game。<br />\n有興趣嘅巴打入黎捧下場，一齊傾下計啦  <br />\n<br />\n今晚11點左右見 <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.twitch.tv/oragejan \" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.twitch.tv%2Foragejan%20&d=t9FZl5ZevfK5fzMtLmZ%2F8jPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=80d2152e\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.twitch.tv/oragejan </a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i2/W4CK8P.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi2%2FW4CK8P.png&h=69cccb5f&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n另外我開左個FB專頁，開台前或者有任何突發事唔開都會Po上FB。<br />\n有時會PO日常野同覺得有趣嘅事，希望巴打們可以入黎比個讚。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/oragejan\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Foragejan&d=t9FZl5ZevfK5fzMtLmZ%2F8jPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=3b497fd9\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/oragejan</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i2/NRSeWz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi2%2FNRSeWz.jpg&h=f4a261d8&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n另外我亦開左個Youtuber Page放開台嘅Backup<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCa49ivSXtdCYwObEq9pRLSg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fchannel%2FUCa49ivSXtdCYwObEq9pRLSg&d=t9FZl5ZevfK5fzMtLmZ%2F8jPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=86ceda95\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCa49ivSXtdCYwObEq9pRLSg</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: pink;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">請各位多多支持，比D錢黎洗下</span></span></div>"},{"pid":"2f74ee23011e14afeba4eb6f354dfd4fcdc6b4a6","tid":386064,"uid":122942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T15:43:34.000Z","msg":"已開<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"697e213aaaaf3a51ea376af8bacc58ab7c67b8ad","tid":386064,"uid":122942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T15:44:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10dc83d35801ad366e618ab00b5937de2b31b094","tid":386064,"uid":122942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T15:45:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6829c7c4af6b8943d72f6398c6180ec2bfe62055","tid":386064,"uid":122942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T15:46:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9594cf66625bab43e320ad121921f69a8dd49380","tid":386064,"uid":122942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T15:47:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e856ee6964949d683ceb49e3b32ee4afe859ea19","tid":386064,"uid":122942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T15:53:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9eb80027fd38123b3fd4ad0ada29cfdd105116b5","tid":386064,"uid":122942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T15:54:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82edf3daac2b74cdeab34cffc6f8d936dccd7e5e","tid":386064,"uid":122942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T15:58:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/s